1
00:00:05,990 --> 00:00:08,686
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,686 --> 00:00:12,141
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,141 --> 00:00:18,334
♫ I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,334 --> 00:00:24,560
♫ I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:31,081
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,081 --> 00:00:36,067
♫ We are always looking forward to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:36,067 --> 00:00:43,367
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,367 --> 00:00:48,391
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,391 --> 00:00:49,904
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,904 --> 00:00:55,667
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,667 --> 00:01:02,167
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,167 --> 00:01:08,434
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,434 --> 00:01:11,788
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:20,459
What are you doing? I'm not done with my handsome photoshoot yet.

15
00:01:20,459 --> 00:01:22,619
What are you up to?

16
00:01:22,619 --> 00:01:25,879
Don't you want to run? Run, then. Compete with me.

17
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:27,720
Who wants to compete with you?

18
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:30,840
What is going on with you?

19
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,319
You're useless!

20
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:34,760
Who's useless? Why are you getting personal?

21
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,859
You think you're all good because you're in the top 10?

22
00:01:36,859 --> 00:01:39,139
I won't argue with you.

23
00:01:39,139 --> 00:01:43,159
Fifty laps. If you can finish it, I'll call you Big Brother.

24
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:48,839
You said it.

25
00:01:48,839 --> 00:01:51,619
I'll give you that chance. Come on.

26
00:01:51,619 --> 00:01:54,900
I can beat you in my slippers!

27
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,000
Who are you insulting?

28
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,799
Who are you insulting here?

29
00:02:10,799 --> 00:02:15,959
I told you I could beat you in my slippers. You're underestimating me.

30
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:23,180
Come on. I'm ready.

31
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:27,500
I'll count to three and we'll run together. Don't say I'm being unfair to you.

32
00:02:29,850 --> 00:02:33,259
Ready. Three, two,

33
00:02:33,259 --> 00:02:35,759
one!

34
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:57,080
You should just call me Big Brother!

35
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:14,680
Old Jin, why don't you just kill me?

36
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:23,199
Whose child is that? He's so hardworking, training so late at night.

37
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:28,299
It'll be nice if Gao Yang works half as hard.

38
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:31,899
No, I have to pull myself together too.

39
00:04:31,899 --> 00:04:35,399
I have to finish the proposal tonight.

40
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,899
Stand up.

41
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:24,060
Didn't you say anyone with legs can run?

42
00:05:25,770 --> 00:05:28,079
Don't push me.

43
00:05:31,170 --> 00:05:33,260
Don't push me.

44
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:04,899
You're too slow. Start running.

45
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,419
Run.

46
00:06:10,419 --> 00:06:14,419
I can do it myself.

47
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,640
Run.

48
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:44,699
I'm not running anymore.

49
00:06:44,699 --> 00:06:47,399
I'm not running anymore. I'm done.

50
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:54,940
Thirty-five laps to go. I'll wait until you get up and finish it.

51
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:58,419
I surrender.

52
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:03,120
No way. I won't let you surrender.

53
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,879
Can't I surrender?

54
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:05,979
No.

55
00:07:05,979 --> 00:07:08,360
You're crazy.

56
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,520
Is running easy?

57
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:33,520
Mi Jia and I have been training in long-distance running since we were 8 years old.

58
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:37,120
It's almost ten years now. We do this every day.

59
00:07:38,290 --> 00:07:40,580
Is that an easy thing to do?

60
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:48,059
You want to do this today, you want to do that tomorrow,

61
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:51,160
you won't achieve anything in your life.

62
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:55,400
What exactly do you want? Have you thought it through yet?

63
00:07:59,340 --> 00:08:00,519
What?

64
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:02,379
What else do you want to say?

65
00:08:05,850 --> 00:08:08,179
You're crazy.

66
00:08:11,402 --> 00:08:21,358
[Episode 11: The Distance Between Us]

67
00:09:05,673 --> 00:09:07,993
[I'm the man who wants to be another Monkey D. Luffy.]
(T/N: reference to anime "One Piece")

68
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,240
Bye.

69
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,779
You're still sleeping?

70
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:38,699
You might catch a cold.

71
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:46,701
[Cultivate twenty excellent athletes in three years]

72
00:09:52,844 --> 00:09:56,901
[Cultivate thirty excellent athletes in three years]

73
00:09:58,410 --> 00:10:01,159
Sometimes you have to push yourself a little.

74
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:10,020
Gao Yang apologized to me.

75
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:13,819
He apologized to you? What did he say?

76
00:10:13,819 --> 00:10:16,600
He said he shouldn't convince me to take the entrance exam for art colleges and told me to focus on my studies.

77
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:20,600
Do you think Gao Yang is capable of figuring that out himself?

78
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:29,079
Why are you looking at me? He figured it out himself.

79
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,519
Where's Gao Yang?

80
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:32,219
In the restroom.

81
00:10:38,860 --> 00:10:43,320
- Meng, here's one. Here's one.
- Okay, let me see.

82
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,999
What are you two doing?

83
00:10:46,999 --> 00:10:48,600
Missing family advertisement.

84
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:53,319
Meng found a few newspapers and magazines that could publish your information. We'll help you look for your parents.

85
00:10:53,319 --> 00:10:57,639
N-No. I-I-I was just saying. D-Don't don't take it seriously.

86
00:10:57,639 --> 00:11:01,380
Why? Don't you want to see them?

87
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:10,219
Auntie said... they... abandoned me. That's why she doesn't want to see them.

88
00:11:10,219 --> 00:11:16,679
Don't think of it like that, Jia. What if that's not true? We can't give up that easily, right?

89
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:20,340
Ye Xiaowen, Mi Jia, Mr. Gao wants to see you in his office.

90
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:22,160
Mr. Gao.

91
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,220
Mi Jia.

92
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,759
By the way, give me the newspaper.

93
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:31,360
Okay. Look at this.

94
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:33,260
Keep your numbers properly.

95
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:35,080
The competition is about to begin.

96
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:38,139
You two should be on a healthy diet, get plenty of sleep, and watch the intensity of your training.

97
00:11:38,139 --> 00:11:40,740
However, this time's qualification trials are a bit difficult.

98
00:11:40,740 --> 00:11:44,779
Only the first place in Tieyuan can advance to the next round.

99
00:11:44,779 --> 00:11:48,139
Only the winner can advance to the next round?

100
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:52,480
But I believe in your abilities.

101
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:58,499
Xiaowen, you have to pay attention to one athlete in the men's group.

102
00:11:58,499 --> 00:11:59,900
W-Who?

103
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:02,719
Chen Sizhe from the No. 2 High School.

104
00:12:02,719 --> 00:12:06,120
His scores are similar to Xiaowen's.

105
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:10,679
But I believe you are the dark horse.

106
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:19,459
Dong. What are you doing, Dong? Wait, wait, let's talk nicely.

107
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:25,139
Wait. You're going to take the college entrance exam soon, right? Aren't you busy?

108
00:12:25,139 --> 00:12:27,039
Yes, that's why I need to see you.

109
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:28,320
Why do you want to see me?

110
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:31,419
Only you can help me with this. I'll smack you if you fail.

111
00:12:31,419 --> 00:12:34,700
What do you need me to do?

112
00:12:37,019 --> 00:12:38,279
Your dad.

113
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:40,579
What about my dad?

114
00:12:40,579 --> 00:12:41,780
- Gao Bin...
- Hello, Mr. Gao.

115
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,499
Hello.

116
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:48,340
Wait, what did Gao Bin do?

117
00:12:51,810 --> 00:12:58,200
Xiaowen, Mr. Gao didn't lie to us. We really have a chance to participate in national games when we come to Tieyuan.

118
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:03,140
If we can get a tuition waiver, I can save a lot of money for Auntie.

119
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:06,159
Only the champion can advance to the next round.

120
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:08,419
W-What did you say?

121
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:13,840
I said the competition is coming soon. We need to increase our training.

122
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:17,840
You're so strong. You can surely get first place in Tieyuan with ease.

123
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:21,400
That Chen something is surely not as good as you.
[Tieyuan High School Long-distance Running Competition]

124
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:26,880
We can't take it lightly. Who knows if something might go wrong?

125
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:36,920
Xiaowen, I know you want to go to the Beijing University of Technology

126
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:42,839
but you didn't dare to mention it before because the tuition is too expensive.

127
00:13:42,839 --> 00:13:46,119
It's all good now. Let's set our goal for the national champion.

128
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:51,559
We'll try to get first place. The Dean will be happy about that, too.

129
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:53,400
You should go back first.

130
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,980
Okay.

131
00:14:04,380 --> 00:14:09,219
Xiaowen, Dong Dawei is a bit strange lately.

132
00:14:14,819 --> 00:14:16,719
I'm talking to you.

133
00:14:18,059 --> 00:14:19,379
Why? Did he bully you again?

134
00:14:19,379 --> 00:14:21,439
No one bullies me.

135
00:14:21,439 --> 00:14:25,380
He asked for my help. The No.3 High School can't function without me.

136
00:14:25,380 --> 00:14:27,879
Enough with the narcissism. It's most likely a trap.

137
00:14:27,879 --> 00:14:32,819
Actually, you're softhearted under that grumpy face. You make a lot of sense.

138
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:35,020
What's wrong with you?

139
00:14:35,020 --> 00:14:37,239
I had another epiphany.

140
00:14:37,239 --> 00:14:40,439
One must have a goal in life.

141
00:14:40,439 --> 00:14:43,299
Xiaowen, what's your goal?

142
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,080
You don't need to know.

143
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,140
Do you want to hear mine?

144
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:47,940
Not interested.

145
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:50,060
It has something to do with you.

146
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:51,399
Just say it.

147
00:14:51,399 --> 00:14:53,579
I want to defeat you.

148
00:14:56,039 --> 00:15:01,479
Only by defeating the strong, can I become stronger. You're my goal.

149
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,200
I don't want to play with you.

150
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:12,999
Who's playing with you?

151
00:15:12,999 --> 00:15:16,639
You're the best around here. Who should I compete with other than you?

152
00:15:17,610 --> 00:15:19,340
- What is this?
- Give it back.

153
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:21,860
- What is this?
- Give it back!

154
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:24,299
I'll give it back if you catch me!

155
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,980
Gao Yang!

156
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:39,759
Stop playing. What if you break it?

157
00:15:41,799 --> 00:15:43,960
Do you know why I won't let you go home?

158
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,860
I don't know.

159
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:50,540
Why don't I think about it when I go home? Mom will be worried.

160
00:15:50,540 --> 00:15:52,940
Stop, come back.

161
00:15:56,170 --> 00:15:57,779
Attention!

162
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,979
Don't threaten me with your mom. In this place, I'm the principal, understand?

163
00:16:03,979 --> 00:16:06,399
Fine, Principal.

164
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:09,380
Well, Principal, what did I do wrong?

165
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:12,400
How did you do on your midterm?

166
00:16:14,039 --> 00:16:15,220
Not bad.

167
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:17,260
You're still trying to fool me?

168
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:21,280
Look at your own report card!

169
00:16:22,340 --> 00:16:24,340
Look on the bottom.

170
00:16:25,579 --> 00:16:28,159
I want to peel off that "Jin" character! Do you understand?

171
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:33,100
That's about the same as last time. I'm keeping it rather steady.

172
00:16:35,450 --> 00:16:37,359
Am I right, dad?

173
00:16:38,679 --> 00:16:41,200
Steadily at the bottom.

174
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:44,360
You have the worst score out of the entire faculty's kids, you know?

175
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:46,699
No, dad. Gao Yang is beneath me.

176
00:16:46,699 --> 00:16:48,579
You're still bringing Gao Yang up?

177
00:16:48,579 --> 00:16:52,840
You hang out with him every day. The two of you were either playing guitar or imitating pop stars.

178
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:55,539
Why don't you learn more from Xiaowen?

179
00:16:55,539 --> 00:16:58,179
Xiaowen should be your goal, you know?

180
00:16:58,179 --> 00:17:00,759
Gao Yang isn't like that anymore.

181
00:17:00,759 --> 00:17:02,240
Jin Beibei,

182
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:06,680
I'm telling you very seriously, you'll be a senior soon.

183
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:10,000
There will be adjustments to your grade soon.

184
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:14,719
After the adjustments, students like you and Gao Yang will immediately show a great disparity from Xiaowen. Do you understand?

185
00:17:14,719 --> 00:17:16,679
What kind of adjustments, dad?

186
00:17:16,679 --> 00:17:19,499
Starting tomorrow, our grade...

187
00:17:19,939 --> 00:17:24,399
You shouldn't ask about that. Just do what you're supposed to do, you know?

188
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:29,200
Finish it within a few days.
[Math Exam Kit]

189
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,620
[Gangzi Repair Shop]

190
00:17:30,620 --> 00:17:33,140
Mr. Gao, let's drink some beer.

191
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:35,180
Dawei's dad, I'm not drinking.

192
00:17:35,180 --> 00:17:37,460
- Why not? Not even a little bit?
- Not today.

193
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:40,019
You came all the way here. If you don't drink,

194
00:17:40,019 --> 00:17:42,279
just suit yourself when you are here.

195
00:17:42,279 --> 00:17:45,819
I advise you not to drink and play mahjong so much.

196
00:17:45,819 --> 00:17:49,579
Dawei will be taking the college entrance exam soon. Try your best to give him a good environment, right?

197
00:17:49,579 --> 00:17:51,299
Yes, yes.

198
00:17:51,299 --> 00:17:54,640
By the way, I brought some study materials for Dawei.

199
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:58,900
Our school's senior grade teachers organized them. I hope this can help Dawei.

200
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:05,600
Mr. Gao, how should I thank you? You're so concerned for this child.

201
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:07,079
Not that I want to put him down,

202
00:18:07,079 --> 00:18:12,240
with his grades, not even God himself can help him. Don't waste your energy on him.

203
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:17,480
Don't say that, Dawei's dad. No matter he has good grades or not, we can't just give up.

204
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:24,099
Besides, the college entrance exam... Dawei, we were just talking about your...

205
00:18:24,099 --> 00:18:28,059
Little bastard, why didn't you greet your teacher? You're so impolite!

206
00:18:28,059 --> 00:18:31,259
- Look at him... It's all my fault for not teaching him properly.
- It's all right.

207
00:18:31,259 --> 00:18:32,840
Sorry about that.

208
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:35,119
For someone like him, he's just asking for a beating.

209
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:36,300
Don't get physical.

210
00:18:36,300 --> 00:18:38,300
What should I do?

211
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,380
What?

212
00:18:41,039 --> 00:18:44,039
Your dad is asking you to set Xiaowen as your goal too?

213
00:18:44,039 --> 00:18:46,659
Let me tell you, don't fight over him with me!

214
00:18:48,559 --> 00:18:49,859
Yes.

215
00:18:50,930 --> 00:18:52,879
That's true.

216
00:18:53,780 --> 00:18:56,679
I need to go. It's time to study. Over.

217
00:19:40,310 --> 00:19:47,460
Since you have been living here for three years, do you know how many streets there are in the city?

218
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:53,610
Yes, there are more than 250 avenues and 157 streets.

219
00:19:53,610 --> 00:19:56,510
Where did you spend your vacation, Billy?

220
00:19:56,510 --> 00:20:00,000
First, I went to Spain, then I visited
[What are you looking at pig head?]

221
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:07,750
France and Germany. At last, I stayed in Japan for a week. 3. May I speak to Robert Teller?

222
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:13,840
"Lovers are always reluctant to part since the ancient times."
(T/N: reference to a poem from the Song Dynasty)

223
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:17,680
"Especially during the cold, desolate autumn."

224
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:20,559
"Where would I find myself as I wake from a hangover?"

225
00:20:20,559 --> 00:20:23,200
"Against the riverbank lined with weeping willows and the waning moon."

226
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:25,700
- "Against the riverbank lined with weeping willows and the waning moon."
- "Years have gone by,

227
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:28,019
- moments of prosperity are nothing but fleeting mirages."
- "Years have gone by,

228
00:20:28,039 --> 00:20:31,840
- moments of prosperity are nothing but fleeting mirages."
- "To whom shall I speak of this ineffably enchanting charm?"

229
00:20:31,840 --> 00:20:33,319
- "Ineffably enchanting charm..."
- "To whom shall I..."

230
00:20:33,319 --> 00:20:35,939
"More ineffably enchanting charm..."

231
00:20:35,939 --> 00:20:38,259
"To whom shall I..."

232
00:20:50,210 --> 00:20:52,019
Where are we?

233
00:20:52,839 --> 00:20:54,319
Why aren't you studying anymore?

234
00:20:54,319 --> 00:20:55,880
I'm going to sleep.

235
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:58,260
It's still so early.

236
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:03,699
You have no willpower at all. I'll study on my own.

237
00:21:10,860 --> 00:21:12,760
Xiaowen.

238
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:16,000
X-Xiaowen, do you hear anything?

239
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:18,179
Hear what?

240
00:21:18,179 --> 00:21:21,240
S-Someone is calling your name.

241
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:24,379
Xiaowen! Mi Jia! Wait for me!

242
00:21:24,379 --> 00:21:26,159
G-G-Gao Yang!

243
00:21:26,159 --> 00:21:27,899
Good morning. Have you had breakfast yet?

244
00:21:27,899 --> 00:21:28,820
Wait for me right here.

245
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:30,600
Have you had breakfast yet?

246
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:34,200
What's wrong?

247
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,840
What are you doing?

248
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:37,340
I'm jogging.

249
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:39,640
We're training. Why are you coming along?

250
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:44,939
But I'm training too. I heard long-distance running can train your willpower. Take me along.

251
00:21:44,939 --> 00:21:47,680
We're preparing for the competition. Don't follow us.

252
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,780
Well, just do your thing and I'll do mine.

253
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:52,060
I'll say it one more time.

254
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:53,939
Stop following us.

255
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:10,839
Xiaowen. Why is Gao Yang here?

256
00:22:10,839 --> 00:22:13,519
- He insists on running with us.
- Well, let's run together.

257
00:22:13,519 --> 00:22:17,000
No, he'll affect our training.

258
00:22:21,860 --> 00:22:26,960
Xiaowen, are you being too nervous?

259
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:29,480
Only the champion can advance to the next round.

260
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:35,740
I have to win. I don't want to beg anyone or let anyone help me again.

261
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:39,720
D-D-Don't give yourself t-too much pressure.

262
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,559
Let's keep running.

263
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:07,000
There are so many questions. When will I ever finish?

264
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:10,500
What's wrong? Principal Jin is forcing you to study?

265
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:18,739
It's not the first day you got bad grades. Why is he starting to get concerned now?

266
00:23:18,739 --> 00:23:21,279
Will you stop being a doomsayer?

267
00:23:21,279 --> 00:23:23,899
Can you stop saying I have bad grades?

268
00:23:23,899 --> 00:23:26,319
It's not my fault. I didn't do well on the exam either.

269
00:23:26,319 --> 00:23:30,279
My dad even confiscated my MP3.

270
00:23:30,279 --> 00:23:33,299
Meng, what should I do?

271
00:23:33,659 --> 00:23:38,500
I have no idea, Beibei. My mom found out I'm writing a novel.

272
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:40,960
She even sold my magazines.

273
00:23:44,359 --> 00:23:47,120
I finally realized it. Xiaowen was the only one who got a good score.

274
00:23:47,120 --> 00:23:50,400
He's running and competing too.

275
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:54,179
Exactly. How does he do that?

276
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:59,359
What are you guys doing? It's so early in the morning.

277
00:23:59,359 --> 00:24:03,999
Can't I just get some sleep? You're so noisy. You think you're the loudest?

278
00:24:05,759 --> 00:24:06,799
Besides,

279
00:24:06,799 --> 00:24:10,219
Ye Xiaowen is just an ordinary person. Don't think too highly of him, okay?

280
00:24:10,219 --> 00:24:12,960
You... Why don't you be as ordinary as him?

281
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:16,820
He's in the top ten students of our grade and he is talented in sports.

282
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:20,720
How can you compare to such a brilliant man?

283
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:26,319
As for Ye Xiaowen, I admit he's smart.

284
00:24:26,319 --> 00:24:28,140
But he's not kind.

285
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:33,000
Last night, I asked him how to solve a problem and he wouldn't even tell me.

286
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:35,859
He's afraid that my scores will surpass him if I learned to solve it.

287
00:24:36,639 --> 00:24:39,640
He doesn't like you and finds you annoying.

288
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,340
Finds you annoying.

289
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:44,940
What do you three little wimpy kids know?

290
00:24:44,940 --> 00:24:48,440
Meng, I'm begging you. Please teach me. I really can't solve that problem.

291
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:51,759
Problem three. Teach me, please.

292
00:24:51,759 --> 00:24:56,799
Look, what's this?

293
00:24:56,799 --> 00:24:59,000
A negative function.

294
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:02,960
Xiaowen, What's your goal?

295
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,880
You don't need to know.

296
00:25:04,880 --> 00:25:06,000
Do you want to hear mine?

297
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:06,939
Not interested.

298
00:25:06,939 --> 00:25:09,640
We're preparing for a competition. Stop following us.

299
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:11,880
Just do your thing and I'll do mine.

300
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:14,060
I'll say it one more time.

301
00:25:14,060 --> 00:25:15,599
Stop following us.

302
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:19,000
Are you being too nervous?

303
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:22,680
Only the champion can advance to the next round. I have to win.

304
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:27,540
I don't want to beg anyone or let anyone help me again.

305
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:31,420
D-D-Don't give yourself t-too much pressure.

306
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:33,220
Substitute it into this formula,

307
00:25:33,220 --> 00:25:34,839
right?

308
00:25:34,839 --> 00:25:36,119
The middle is 0 to 1...

309
00:25:36,119 --> 00:25:37,060
Gao Yang, where are you going?

310
00:25:37,060 --> 00:25:39,060
Draw it out.

311
00:25:39,799 --> 00:25:41,999
- Here.
- Yes.

312
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:54,740
All athletes, get on your marks.

313
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:56,779
Ready.

314
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:21,519
Go, go, go!

315
00:26:27,436 --> 00:26:29,595
[Tieyuan Long-distance Running Competition]

316
00:26:38,259 --> 00:26:40,459
What are you doing here?

317
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:44,720
What?

318
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:47,759
Well, what shoe brand do you like?

319
00:26:47,759 --> 00:26:49,019
Why do you ask that?

320
00:26:49,019 --> 00:26:52,279
You're about to compete. I want to gift you a pair of shoes.

321
00:26:55,119 --> 00:26:56,719
I don't need them.

322
00:26:58,480 --> 00:27:02,559
Look at your shoes. They are falling apart. Let me buy you a pair of shoes.

323
00:27:02,559 --> 00:27:04,479
I don't want you to spend money.

324
00:27:06,119 --> 00:27:08,119
What do you want, then? Just tell me.

325
00:27:08,119 --> 00:27:10,199
I want to be alone.

326
00:27:10,199 --> 00:27:12,659
Can't I care about you?

327
00:27:12,659 --> 00:27:17,200
I don't need your care or your money. Can't I just stay alone for a while?

328
00:27:18,140 --> 00:27:21,459
He doesn't like you and finds you annoying.

329
00:27:22,140 --> 00:27:24,040
You're so annoying.

330
00:27:24,839 --> 00:27:26,539
You're so annoying.

331
00:27:27,519 --> 00:27:29,319
You're so annoying!

332
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:34,440
Ye Xiaowen, do you find me annoying?

333
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:36,119
Are we friends?

334
00:27:36,119 --> 00:27:37,680
If you say so.

335
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:40,079
What do you mean if I say so?

336
00:27:40,079 --> 00:27:42,559
Gao Yang, we're different.

337
00:27:42,559 --> 00:27:46,800
Friends aren't important to me. I only care about the competition now. I want to win. I need this to go to the university.

338
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:48,480
Do you understand?

339
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:50,180
What am I to you?

340
00:27:51,100 --> 00:27:52,800
A roommate.

341
00:27:56,799 --> 00:27:58,799
You're treating me like a roommate?

342
00:28:00,979 --> 00:28:06,620
Hey, Roommate, I'm sorry. Sorry I've bothered you. From now on, I won't bother you again.

343
00:28:21,279 --> 00:28:23,180
- Did you see the game last night?
- Girls should eat less sugar.

344
00:28:23,180 --> 00:28:26,259
- A winning goal at minute 94.
- I didn't sleep at all.

345
00:28:26,259 --> 00:28:27,819
Excuse me.

346
00:28:28,799 --> 00:28:29,759
Go ahead. What's wrong?

347
00:28:29,759 --> 00:28:31,499
I want to change seats.

348
00:28:31,499 --> 00:28:32,519
Why?

349
00:28:32,519 --> 00:28:34,039
I'm tired of sitting here.

350
00:28:34,039 --> 00:28:36,680
Isn't that a coincidence? Perfect timing. I have an announcement to make.

351
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:41,219
From today onward, we'll have new classes for our grade. That will perfectly fulfill your need.

352
00:28:41,219 --> 00:28:43,620
Why do we suddenly have different classes?

353
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:46,720
We are going to establish an elite class in our grade.

354
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:51,760
The top 30 students of our grade based on the midterm scores will be put into this elite class to enhance their studies.

355
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:54,359
Let me announce the students from our class.

356
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:57,620
Ye Xiaowen, Tian Meng,

357
00:28:57,620 --> 00:28:59,960
Zhang Kaiying, Wang Xiaoyu,

358
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:04,040
and Tian Yu. These five students will be in the elite class. Let's give them some encouragement.

359
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:10,060
Meng, if you go to the elite class, who's going to be my desk mate?

360
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:15,419
All right, all right. Stop wailing as if it's goodbye forever.

361
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:18,440
Don't take it as unfair treatment.

362
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:21,399
Students of various phases require different learning techniques.

363
00:29:21,399 --> 00:29:26,019
Our mission is to make sure everyone gets a good score on their exam and goes to a good college, right?

364
00:29:26,019 --> 00:29:30,759
Although some students with outstanding scores are about to leave our class, we will still be on the same floor.

365
00:29:30,759 --> 00:29:34,720
You'll still be good friends. Go visit them and exchange learning experiences.

366
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,920
All right, let's get back to class.

367
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,300
This is our last class together?

368
00:29:45,799 --> 00:29:47,599
Meng,

369
00:29:47,599 --> 00:29:49,920
I didn't pay attention in class before

370
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:53,979
because I know I can ask you if I don't understand anything after class.

371
00:29:53,979 --> 00:29:57,939
Now that you're leaving, who am I supposed to ask?

372
00:29:58,820 --> 00:30:00,640
I can hardly look after myself.

373
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:06,799
In a competitive world like the elite class, grades mean everything.

374
00:30:06,799 --> 00:30:09,739
With my grades, I would be at the bottom of the class when I get there.

375
00:30:09,739 --> 00:30:13,590
A student with bad grades in the elite class is still a student with bad grades.

376
00:30:14,540 --> 00:30:18,039
No wonder my dad was pushing me so much recently.

377
00:30:18,039 --> 00:30:21,020
It was because I didn't get into the elite class and I embarrassed him.

378
00:30:21,020 --> 00:30:22,330
- That's right.
- Yes.

379
00:30:22,330 --> 00:30:24,960
Your dad is the principal and your scores are at the bottom of our class.

380
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,780
It's hardly convincing for him to be in that position.

381
00:30:26,780 --> 00:30:29,199
Zhao Jiabao, I'll kill you!

382
00:30:29,199 --> 00:30:31,740
If you kill me, you'll be one place lower. What's the point?

383
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:35,820
I don't want to argue with you.

384
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:42,599
Xiaowen, I'll leave Meng to you. Take care of her.

385
00:30:42,599 --> 00:30:44,499
What's wrong?

386
00:30:44,499 --> 00:30:46,900
They must've had an argument.

387
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:49,499
Why?

388
00:30:49,499 --> 00:30:51,779
It's so obvious. You can't tell?

389
00:30:52,540 --> 00:30:56,680
It must be because Gao Yang can't catch up to Xiaowen now that he's in the elite class.

390
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:04,560
Wanwan, you're so brilliant. You can even rank at the top of the elite class.

391
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:09,059
I actually didn't do my best this time. Otherwise, I would be the first place.

392
00:31:14,970 --> 00:31:20,359
I told you to be my friend and you just had to hang out with Jin Beibei and the other idiots.

393
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:22,340
This is good. You've stopped at their level.

394
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,580
You!

395
00:31:23,580 --> 00:31:25,699
Xiaowen is in my class now.

396
00:31:25,699 --> 00:31:29,020
If you have anything to say to him, I can help you relay the message.

397
00:31:30,340 --> 00:31:33,700
Mi Jia, you're going to Class 3 too?

398
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:36,300
What a coincidence. I'm going there too.

399
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:39,060
Isn't that really serendipitous?

400
00:31:41,060 --> 00:31:43,160
I'll see you in Class 3.

401
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:47,900
My dad was right after all.

402
00:31:47,900 --> 00:31:51,060
There's a disparity between Xiaowen and us now.

403
00:31:52,070 --> 00:31:55,080
And between Meng and us too.

404
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:59,259
I'm just going to the elite class for a few days. Maybe I'll come back after.

405
00:31:59,259 --> 00:32:03,359
You can't do that. You have to work hard and stay in the elite class.

406
00:32:03,359 --> 00:32:06,600
That's right. Y-Y-You have to beat Niu Wanwan and piss her off.

407
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:07,880
That's right.

408
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:12,119
I can't beat her. You should put your hopes on Xiaowen.

409
00:32:12,119 --> 00:32:13,639
Don't mention him.

410
00:32:14,550 --> 00:32:17,540
Isn't Xiaowen your idol? Why can't we mention him?

411
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:20,380
I'm not good enough for him.

412
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:22,160
Did you two have a fight?

413
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:23,739
How could we?

414
00:32:23,739 --> 00:32:28,100
He's a good student. He has no time to fight with me.

415
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:29,860
Here's the thing.

416
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:34,579
Let me tell you, as students with bad grades, we should unite together

417
00:32:34,579 --> 00:32:38,539
and not hang out with the elite students. They will look down upon us.

418
00:32:38,539 --> 00:32:40,900
Meng, don't listen to him. He's not talking about you.

419
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:43,780
That's right. Meng, you're a good one.

420
00:32:43,780 --> 00:32:47,900
Although you're doing well now, you didn't forget us.

421
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:53,879
Come on, let's wish Tian Meng smooth sailing in the elite class.

422
00:32:56,251 --> 00:32:58,343
[Elite Class]

423
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:03,559
Which college should I go by recommendation, Beijing University or Tsinghua University?

424
00:33:03,559 --> 00:33:05,100
I'm worried about that too.

425
00:33:05,100 --> 00:33:07,480
I think the School of Management at Beijing University is nice,

426
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:10,420
but Tsinghua University's School of Automation wants me too.

427
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:27,400
Don't sit there. It's not your seat.

428
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:32,540
- Isn't it empty?
- Who told you it's empty?

429
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:38,860
Tian Meng, I'll give you a piece of advice.

430
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:42,799
With your grades, you might not be in the elite class after the next exam.

431
00:33:42,799 --> 00:33:44,839
So, study really hard.

432
00:33:44,839 --> 00:33:46,620
Let me give you a piece of advice too.

433
00:33:46,620 --> 00:33:51,839
Women won't like a pretentious woman like you, men also won't like that either.

434
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:11,380
Ye Xiaowen,

435
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:17,160
sit over here.

436
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:36,360
Hello, my name is Niu Wanwan.

437
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:40,860
I think we've met before at the Top 10 Students Award Ceremony.

438
00:34:41,490 --> 00:34:43,760
This cake is for you.

439
00:35:05,930 --> 00:35:10,039
Hello, Everyone. Let me introduce myself. My name is Piao Jiutong.

440
00:35:10,039 --> 00:35:13,539
I'm the leader of the Korean Club. Hello, Everyone.

441
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:17,640
Mi Jia, we meet again.

442
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:20,819
I told you there's a serendipitous connection between us.

443
00:35:23,190 --> 00:35:28,179
Piao Jiutong, if you harass Mi Jia again, I'll smack you!

444
00:35:28,179 --> 00:35:30,639
You have bad grades. Be quiet.

445
00:35:30,639 --> 00:35:34,900
Classmates, Class 3 generally has pretty terrible grades.

446
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:37,240
Anyone who wants to improve their grades can come see me.

447
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:39,019
Do you think I can't set you straight?

448
00:35:39,019 --> 00:35:42,519
Stop, stop. Don't be impulsive.

449
00:35:42,519 --> 00:35:44,939
By the way, how's Principal Jin lately?

450
00:35:44,939 --> 00:35:50,659
Maybe I should go upstairs to visit him tonight and give him a report on the recent situation in school.

451
00:35:51,410 --> 00:35:54,160
My dad misses you very much too.

452
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,119
Gao, you rule.

453
00:36:00,119 --> 00:36:01,939
Put an end to his arrogance.

454
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:07,280
Piao, pay me the 10 Yuan you owe me from last time.

455
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,579
Stop putting it off.

456
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:14,240
What kind of people are in Class 3?
[Student on duty]

457
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:22,300
Slow down. There's more.

458
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,100
Delicious. So delicious.

459
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:30,799
I'm telling you, at the time, all high school principals in Tieyuan were there.

460
00:36:30,799 --> 00:36:33,900
The director general just directly asked to use our proposal.

461
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:39,520
He said we must do that to prepare for the Olympic Games and improve high school sports.

462
00:36:39,520 --> 00:36:41,199
So, everything went well?

463
00:36:41,199 --> 00:36:42,800
Very well.

464
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:46,820
Therefore, Coach Gao, you have to establish the track and field team to prepare for the Olympic Games soon.

465
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:52,739
Wait, Jin, let's deliberate again.

466
00:36:52,739 --> 00:36:56,740
Can I not be the coach? I have two kids at home.

467
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:59,600
No. I have two kids too.

468
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:02,340
By next week, I want to see a brand new track and field team.

469
00:37:02,340 --> 00:37:06,580
What do you mean next week? Have you discussed it with me?

470
00:37:06,580 --> 00:37:09,760
By the way, the Tieyuan TV station is coming for an interview soon.

471
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:12,819
You should do some grooming. Don't look too shabby.

472
00:37:13,570 --> 00:37:17,720
Jin, how could you do that? I... Where am I going to find the team?

473
00:37:17,720 --> 00:37:19,660
I don't care.

474
00:37:21,530 --> 00:37:24,379
Don't eat so many instant noodles. It's not healthy.

475
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:36,540
Gao Yang, what are you looking at?

476
00:37:38,260 --> 00:37:43,260
I'm thinking, is she holding a pigeon or a bird?

477
00:37:43,260 --> 00:37:44,640
Pigeons are birds, right?

478
00:37:44,640 --> 00:37:46,239
Exactly.

479
00:37:46,239 --> 00:37:50,280
Are you waiting for Xiaowen?

480
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:53,879
What Xiaowen? Why should I wait for him?

481
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:57,360
Then why aren't you going home?

482
00:37:57,360 --> 00:38:01,939
Go home and study. When we all get into the elite class, you'll be left out.

483
00:38:01,939 --> 00:38:04,719
"Cows are flying in the sky". Let's go, Jia.
(T/N: means he's boasting)

484
00:38:04,719 --> 00:38:05,900
- Where?
- Let's go study.

485
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:08,080
Let's go. Are you really looking for them?

486
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:25,840
It's been a whole day. Have you made a decision?

487
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:28,040
About what?

488
